=  & 1.1913 \pm 1.96\times \sqrt{\frac{1}{198}\ -\frac{1}{532}+\frac{1}{128}-\frac{1}{1132}}\\ 
=  & (0.9944,\ 1.3883 )\end{aligned}$$

